name: The cart woman / La mujer del carrito
description:
My name is Victor Vivas, I dedicate myself to street photography with the intention of capturing moments that show what we are from the culture and with the intention of producing empathy towards the other.

This photograph is part of the project Con los pies en la calle with your purchase you collaborate so that I can continue with this initiative and be able to improve the teams with which I work.

The woman in the cart was taken in the city of Barquisimeto, Venezuela.
